{"tid":828130,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"NS買付費會員下載免費遊戲鎖台灣鎖中國但唔鎖香港","createTime":"2018-09-19T12:27:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-25T17:52:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9d413878e36fee28dc62e03432be640b4a86c544","tid":828130,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:27:13.000Z","msg":"如果是日本海外全鎖我還比較能接受，問題現在是連香港都沒鎖，就只鎖中國跟台灣&hellip;真的覺得任天堂激怒台灣玩家的功力堪稱一流啊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我們一直在笑對岸翻牆才能用FB <br />\n現在台日友好要翻牆才能玩快變化石的冷飯<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?page=2&amp;bsn=31587&amp;snA=8936\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fpage%3D2%26bsn%3D31587%26snA%3D8936&d=5Yy3A3KNChMTIb5I5eF7g9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=a7bb4c6f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?page=2&amp;bsn=31587&amp;snA=8936</a><br />\n<br />\n轉珠院 不肯定是誤中副車，要鎖中國但把台灣也鎖了，還是忘了鎖香港<br />\n7 小時前<br />\n轉珠院 現在的情況就是中國和台灣也鎖了，但香港沒事<br />\n7 小時前<br />\n<br />\n抓到了 任天堂支持一中<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31587&amp;snA=9096\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.gamer.com.tw%2FC.php%3Fbsn%3D31587%26snA%3D9096&d=5Yy3A3KNChMTIb5I5eF7g9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=bec39e20\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.gamer.com.tw/C.php?bsn=31587&amp;snA=9096</a>"},{"pid":"2cceedbf8932c31abdae3b2b90e07abf4d1893c6","tid":828130,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:33:28.000Z","msg":"マダオ冰雨 所以只擋台灣IP不擋香港IP的意思嗎？"},{"pid":"4a12b9ee6877e1d47ea18d0814dae23dc19c9aca","tid":828130,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-19T12:34:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://aqua.komica.org/27/pixmicat.php?res=719687\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faqua.komica.org%2F27%2Fpixmicat.php%3Fres%3D719687&d=5Yy3A3KNChMTIb5I5eF7g9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=3cabbdc7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https: